(81, 7, 'leadership_block_2_leadership_description', 'Herb is a master when it comes to mapping state-of-the-art technology to specific business challenges. With 30+ years of experience creating, operating and marketing technical products and services at companies like Bell Atlantic, Data General, and Hyperdesk, his record of success encompasses both fields - marketing and technology. He resides just outside Boston, Massachusetts.'),
