(316, 41, '_careers_block_2_careers_title', 'field_5bed03bc9c536'),
(317, 41, 'careers_block_2_careers_description', 'You’ll get a Silicon Valley development culture, with opportunities in a global company that takes care of its people. Compensation is competitive and includes paid holidays and holiday bonuses. You’ll enjoy subsidized lunch, free snacks and beverages, frequent team activities/outings, and socially-conscious employee initiatives that make a difference in our community.'),
